 I'm thankful, God, that,

1037
00:45:51,180 --> 00:45:56,400
 God, though I and though we can be better,

1038
00:45:56,400 --> 00:45:59,460
 you, God, cannot be.

1039
00:45:59,460 --> 00:46:01,060
 You are so good.

1040
00:46:01,060 --> 00:46:02,540
 You are so faithful.

1041
00:46:02,540 --> 00:46:03,980
 You are so kind.

1042
00:46:03,980 --> 00:46:08,580
 And God, you are so very slow to anger.

1043
00:46:09,780 --> 00:46:13,340
 You want all to come to the knowledge of your mercy.

1044
00:46:13,340 --> 00:46:16,820
 You want all God to bend the knee in repentance.

1045
00:46:16,820 --> 00:46:20,520
 And so God, I'm asking that you would do that tonight.

1046
00:46:20,520 --> 00:46:24,380
 I'm praying, God, that here in this moment,

1047
00:46:24,380 --> 00:46:26,980
 as we turn back to worship,

1048
00:46:26,980 --> 00:46:30,780
 you'd save us from stealing out of the room

1049
00:46:30,780 --> 00:46:33,020
 and racing into our evening.

1050
00:46:33,020 --> 00:46:35,060
 You would save us from making excuses

1051
00:46:35,060 --> 00:46:37,580
 about why, God, we're not going to respond

1052
00:46:37,580 --> 00:46:39,540
 when we know it is you that is asking,

1053
00:46:39,540 --> 00:46:42,020
 that is calling, that is seeking.

1054
00:46:42,020 --> 00:46:45,380
 I pray, God, you'd save us from ourself.

1055
00:46:45,380 --> 00:46:47,140
 And for some of us, God, that means tonight

1056
00:46:47,140 --> 00:46:48,660
 we reach the end of ourself,

1057
00:46:48,660 --> 00:46:50,380
 that we find the beginning of you.

1058
00:46:50,380 --> 00:46:52,020
 God, meet with us now.

1059
00:46:52,020 --> 00:46:54,220
 Move amongst us, please.

1060
00:46:54,220 --> 00:46:58,420
 And won't we know you are so very patient.

1061
00:46:58,420 --> 00:47:02,860
 And God, we're meant to be so very repentant.

1062
00:47:02,860 --> 00:47:03,820
 We love you.

1063
00:47:03,820 --> 00:47:05,420
 It's in Christ's name we pray.

1064
00:47:05,420 --> 00:47:06,260
 Amen.

